# CSE412Project
Restaurant Booking System

npm init -y: run this before running the website

npm install express mongoose body-parser

run "node app.js" interminal

it should provide a address that you can open it in the browser

User Manual:
1. Log in to this system, click LogIn button on right top.
<img width="1435" alt="Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 8 59 43 PM" src="https://github.com/Slooogen/CSE412Project/assets/78095430/fdc546f1-57a7-47c0-87b7-840d8bd99ee6">

2. Click the restaurant to look details information: like food pictures and opening hours.
 <img width="1440" alt="Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 9 01 26 PM" src="https://github.com/Slooogen/CSE412Project/assets/78095430/769f7051-8dbb-4a4e-922d-134705e04987">

3. Use the bottom button "reserve" on each restaurant page to make a reservation and fill out the table.
<img width="1428" alt="Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 9 03 10 PM" src="https://github.com/Slooogen/CSE412Project/assets/78095430/cde28690-ea96-4912-aaa4-006ad359d11c">

4. View all your reservations on Table menus, which is on the left top of the home page.
<img width="1284" alt="Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 9 04 19 PM" src="https://github.com/Slooogen/CSE412Project/assets/78095430/69f32b51-0f4c-4d45-898f-7839c3f90ad2">
